com.redhat.rhn.testing
Class ForwardWrapper

java.lang.Object
  ActionForward
      com.redhat.rhn.testing.ForwardWrapper

public class ForwardWrapper
extends ActionForward

A decorator for a org.apache.struts.action.ActionForward. In addition to decorating a forward, this class adds the capability of getting parameters from the forward's path with getParam(java.lang.String) and getLongParam(java.lang.String).
